<HEADLINE>
<P>
A FINANCIAL PLANNER CAN BE A GOLD MINE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
I feel that the article about financial planners ("Financial Planner, Broker 
Offer Different Services," Dec. 3) in your special section deprecates financial 
planners by showing a negative and distrustful attitude without giving any 
mention of the many worthwhile benefits of utilizing such a professional. 
</P>
<P>
As the owner of a retail showroom, I have found the complexity of coordinating 
my attorney, accountant, investments, tax planning, personal health insurance 
and group health benefits an almost impossible task without the guidance of my 
financial planner. 
</P>
<P>
My financial planner implements the various financial products he recommends 
and sells insurance policies. My time is much more effective while utilizing a 
financial planner. 
</P>
<P>
Good financial planners should be well paid; they are literally worth their 
weight in gold. 
</P>
<P>
NICHOLAS PAUL HERTNECK 
</P>
<P>
Laguna Beach 
</P>
