</P>
<P>
ERNST &amp; YOUNG'S ARTHUR YOUNG TAX GUIDE 1990 by Ernst and Young, edited by 
Peter W. Bernstein (Ballantine: $11.95). This sixth annual edition includes 
usable 1989 federal tax forms, a tax calendar and organizer and 40 of the most 
easily overlooked deductions. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
