POLITICAL ASYLUM; FUGITIVES; VATICAN -- EMBASSIES; UNITED STATES -- FOREIGN 
RELATIONS -- VATICAN; UNITED STATES -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- PANAMA 
</P>
